dict.acceptation: 快的；走得快；感光快的；紧的；
（比准确的时间或宣布的时间）快；迅速地；紧紧地；彻底地；
禁食期，斋戒期；断食，节食；

sent.orig: The protocol is called FAST, standing for Fast Active queue management Scalable Transmission Control Protocol( TCP).
sent.trans: 这个协议就是FAST,也就是快速积极行列管理的可升级的传输控制协议。

sent.orig: This provides fail-fast behavior, rather than non-deterministic behavior in the face of concurrent modification iteration.
sent.trans: 一旦在遍历过程中遇到同步修改时，会导致fail-fast特性而不是非确定的行为。

sent.orig: The geodesic meshed cable-net structure was used to support reflector of the Five-hundred-meter Telescope (FAST) .
sent.trans: 采用整体索网作为大射电望远镜(FAST)反射面的支承结构，网格划分形式为短程线型。

sent.orig: Can a Carrier become an approved FAST carrier without being a C-TPAT participant?
sent.trans: 问：不加入C-TPAT,能否被批准成为FAST承运人？

sent.orig: Do I have to join both the C-TPAT and FAST Programs to receive the most benefits?
sent.trans: 问：我是否必须都要加入C-TPAT和FAST以获取最大的利益？
